name: Saitama Inu (SAITAMA)
description:
Welcome to SAITAMA INU, a community-driven platform that promotes global financial wellbeing by empowering the youth to be in control of their money and create their own wealth opportunities. 

From every transaction of SAITAMA INU, there is an automatic 2% distribution reward to the holders and another 2% is burnt. It means that just by investing and holding SAITAMA INU in their wallets our community is earning passive income.
